venn.optim
Interface IOptimizer

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractOptimizer, EvolutionaryOptimizer, EvolutionaryOptimizerV1, SwarmOptimizer
public interface IOptimizer

Optimizes an abstract thing. The caller has to perform the following steps

  1. optimizer.setUp()
  2. while( ! optimizer.endCondition() ) { optimizer.optimize(); }
  3. optimizer.tearDown()
One possibility for this is OptimizerWorker.

Author:
muellera
